{"tid":2133616,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［旺角騷亂］盧建民上訴被拒","createTime":"2020-07-31T07:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T08:35:43.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3c50595d66373853b18395d60d666f144c2ed2","tid":2133616,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"【最新】旺角騷亂案暴動罪成判囚七年的盧建民，上訴庭拒絕批出他就定罪及刑期上訴至終審法院的證明書<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=17932&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D17932%26refer%3DShare&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16RE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=8516c735\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D17932%26refer%3DShare&h=c0fece38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=17932&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"be2869e9b7253145f078026b9346d5c32936519c","tid":2133616,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mj8POj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mj8POj.jpg&h=7ba23851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高等法院上訴庭拒絕就盧建民的定罪及刑期覆核批出上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n盧建民因四年前參加魚蛋革命被判暴動罪成，重囚七年。<br />\n<br />\n終極上訴許可被拒，代表三人暴動案的法律程序畫上句號。<br />\n<br />\n相關判詞<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞"},{"pid":"5776e04b9d5ea73b78219adb5c2a293cfa2caae7","tid":2133616,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ebaa6496c9c50cc2260f909678408a750208a2c","tid":2133616,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eeb3fcff80247d3a7f849dcb2139103c6cd292","tid":2133616,"uid":307827,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"On9法治 斬撚到人入icu坐3年高尚情操<br />\n對抗暴政就比人判暴動坐7年<br />\n法律根本就係打壓人民既統治工具"},{"pid":"be0a673d01613e3c3e827e711722fb59f3f543a1","tid":2133616,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"#高等法院第一庭<br />\n#潘兆初高等法院首席法官<br />\n#朱芬齡上訴庭法官<br />\n#彭偉昌上訴庭法官<br />\n<br />\n盧建民(32) <br />\n<br />\n#宣布裁決 (魚蛋革命&mdash;是否批出終極上訴許可)<br />\n<br />\n定罪上訴<br />\n刑罰上訴<br />\n上訴庭認為暴動罪的罪責應依據群眾而非個人的暴力程度，而利用其他案件的量刑作比較亦非務實做法，裁定問題沒有可辯之處，並非屬於重大法律觀點，故此駁回刑罰上訴許可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭拒絕批出終極上訴許可<br />\n<br />\n[英文判案書按此]（轉載自司法機構）"},{"pid":"d3797202af8f47b86b5da381ba9dbbd5347b7958","tid":2133616,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be2869e9b7253145f078026b9346d5c32936519c","tid":2133616,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mj8POj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mj8POj.jpg&h=7ba23851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高等法院上訴庭拒絕就盧建民的定罪及刑期覆核批出上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n盧建民因四年前參加魚蛋革命被判暴動罪成，重囚七年。<br />\n<br />\n終極上訴許可被拒，代表三人暴動案的法律程序畫上句號。<br />\n<br />\n相關判詞<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:09:32.000Z","msg":"邊個出新聞稿，可以直接上訴"},{"pid":"e98a3850310725c99c255ce352322c90b7426617","tid":2133616,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5566db0bfc7a3c2a36cb5985f74882bb7683382","tid":2133616,"uid":106672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3797202af8f47b86b5da381ba9dbbd5347b7958","tid":2133616,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be2869e9b7253145f078026b9346d5c32936519c","tid":2133616,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mj8POj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mj8POj.jpg&h=7ba23851&s={SIZE}\" /><